Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:02.05,Title,,0,0,0,,{\1cE6E84B\4c7582C2\3aFF\fn@方正屏显雅宋_GBK\fr-90\fs120\fsp50\blur3\pos(1710,568)}刘海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:40.90,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fn@华康手札体W7-A\fr-90\bord1\1c7C71FF\3c7B71F5\shad0\fs80\pos(1032,570)\fsp10}情人节
